      "body" : "It's counterintuitive to most people that Bitcoin Core will refuse to use non-standard ports as anything but a last resort, does the option label need a GUI label or a confirmation popup to reflect this? I suspect a lot of people will be mystified otherwise that they don't get any incoming connections after changing a fairly innocuous looking option. ",
