      "body" : "We need a better protection to not run into a startup termination if the user did enter a invalid port. IIRC the `QIntValidator` still allows one to enter `0` as port number which will very likely result in a locked Bitcoin-QT (startup will stop because of a invalid port). Haven't tested although.\r\nMaybe check: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/7025",
